<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Réinitialisation du mot de passe</title>
  <style>
    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Sans:wght@400;500;600&family=DM+Serif+Display&display=swap');

    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

    body {
      background-color: #0f0f12;
      font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
      color: #e2e2e8;
      padding: 40px 16px;
    }

    .wrapper {
      max-width: 560px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    /* Header */
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 32px;
    }

    .logo {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .logo-icon {
      width: 36px;
      height: 36px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e8c97e, #c8993e);
      border-radius: 8px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .logo-icon svg {
      width: 20px;
      height: 20px;
      fill: #0f0f12;
    }

    .logo-text {
      font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
      font-size: 20px;
      color: #e8c97e;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }

    /* Card */
    .card {
      background: #18181f;
      border: 1px solid #2a2a36;
      border-radius: 20px;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .card-top {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e1c2e 0%, #1a1824 100%);
      padding: 48px 48px 36px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #2a2a36;
      position: relative;
    }

    .card-top::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: -60px;
      right: -60px;
      width: 200px;
      height: 200px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(232,201,126,0.08) 0%, transparent 70%);
      border-radius: 50%;
    }

    .icon-wrap {
      width: 56px;
      height: 56px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(232,201,126,0.15), rgba(200,153,62,0.05));
      border: 1px solid rgba(232,201,126,0.25);
      border-radius: 14px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .icon-wrap svg {
      width: 26px;
      height: 26px;
      stroke: #e8c97e;
      fill: none;
      stroke-width: 1.75;
      stroke-linecap: round;
      stroke-linejoin: round;
    }

    .card-top h1 {
      font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
      font-size: 26px;
      color: #f0f0f5;
      font-weight: 400;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      line-height: 1.3;
    }

    .card-top p {
      font-size: 15px;
      color: #8888a0;
      line-height: 1.65;
    }

    /* Body */
    .card-body {
      padding: 36px 48px;
    }

    .cta-btn {
      display: block;
      width: 100%;
      padding: 16px 24px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e8c97e, #c8993e);
      color: #0f0f12;
      text-decoration: none;
      text-align: center;
      font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.3px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
      transition: opacity 0.2s;
    }

    .divider {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .divider-line {
      flex: 1;
      height: 1px;
      background: #2a2a36;
    }

    .divider-text {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #55556a;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .link-box {
      background: #0f0f12;
      border: 1px solid #2a2a36;
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 14px 16px;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
      word-break: break-all;
    }

    .link-box a {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #7878a8;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    /* Notice */
    .notice {
      display: flex;
      gap: 12px;
      align-items: flex-start;
      background: rgba(232,201,126,0.05);
      border: 1px solid rgba(232,201,126,0.12);
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 14px 16px;
    }

    .notice svg {
      width: 16px;
      height: 16px;
      stroke: #e8c97e;
      fill: none;
      stroke-width: 2;
      stroke-linecap: round;
      stroke-linejoin: round;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      margin-top: 2px;
    }

    .notice p {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #8888a0;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .notice strong {
      color: #e8c97e;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    /* Footer */
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 28px 16px 0;
    }

    .footer p {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #44445a;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .footer a {
      color: #55556a;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .footer .brand {
      margin-top: 16px;
      font-size: 11px;
      color: #33333f;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrapper">

    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="header">
      <div class="logo">
        <div class="logo-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5zM2 17l10 5 10-5M2 12l10 5 10-5"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <span class="logo-text">M-TEC Fleet Manager</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Card -->
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-top">
        <div class="icon-wrap">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="11" rx="2" ry="2"/>
            <path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h1>Réinitialisation<br/>du mot de passe</h1>
        <p>Nous avons reçu une demande de réinitialisation de votre mot de passe. Cliquez sur le bouton ci-dessous pour continuer.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="card-body">
        <a href="{{resetLink}}" class="cta-btn">
          Réinitialiser mon mot de passe
        </a>

        <div class="divider">
          <div class="divider-line"></div>
          <span class="divider-text">ou copiez ce lien</span>
          <div class="divider-line"></div>
        </div>

        <div class="link-box">
          <a href="{{resetLink}}">{{resetLink}}</a>
        </div>

        <div class="notice">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/>
            <line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12" y2="12"/>
            <line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12.01" y2="16"/>
          </svg>
          <p>Ce lien est valable pendant <strong>30 minutes</strong>. Si vous n'avez pas demandé cette réinitialisation, vous pouvez ignorer cet e-mail en toute sécurité.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <div class="footer">
      <p>
        Cet e-mail a été envoyé par <a href="#">M-TEC Fleet Manager</a>.<br/>
        Si vous avez des questions, contactez notre <a href="#">support</a>.
      </p>
      <p class="brand">© 2026 M-TEC — Tous droits réservés</p>
    </div>

  </div>
</body>
</html>
```
